---
title: Cherry-Glazed Chicken & Veggie Couscous with Roasted Almonds
description: Let this cherry red glaze get you into a festive spirit while it coats tender chicken breast and accompanies a filling bed of Israeli couscous. All tossed with warm roasted veggies to bring further richness to the dish, you’ll be singing songs of delight after every bite.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
